name: Shugabuzz
description: The Shugabuzz is the most eccentric of the Shugafam, mainly reflected in its unusual choice of instrument. Other peculiar traits include its facial fur stylings, and a diet of almost exclusively saggle nuts (which everyone else says taste like rocks and give its limbs their smoky-purple coloration).
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 1 day 11 hr, Enhanced Time: 1 day 2 hr 15 min
